Give your AI assistant project memory

Your AI tools forget context between sessions. recuerd0 fixes that — it gives them persistent memory that you control.

Claude Code

Add the recuerd0 skill to your project's CLAUDE.md:

  ## Recuerd0 Knowledge Base

  Use the `/recuerd0` skill to search project knowledge.
  recuerd0 search "query terms" --pretty

Claude Code will automatically search your memories for relevant context before reading source code.

Other AI tools

Any tool that supports REST APIs or MCP servers can connect to recuerd0. The recuerd0-agents repository has ready-made configurations for Cursor, ChatGPT, and other tools.

Integration Guide: https://github.com/maquina-app/recuerd0-agents

Your memories are served read-only to AI tools by default. You stay in control.
